defined_terms.definition_excerpt:
"New instructional facility" includes:
(A) a newly constructed instructional facility;
(B) a repurposed instructional facility;
(C) a leased facility operating for the first time as an instructional facility with a minimum lease term of not less than 10 years; and
(D) a renovated portion of an instructional facility to be used for the first time to provide high-cost and undersubscribed career and technology education programs, as determined by the commissioner.
